metadata.name: youlovepaper
metadata.description:
Paper, hails from the most autonomous regions of the Rocky Mountains. 

Conceived in a 1948 Chevy Panel Van after a Prince concert, Paper began playing the blues at 2. When Paper dropped the needle to scratch his first record he fell in love with Hip Hop.

He began building a name for himself playing house parties, unaware that this path lead him to being dubbed the greatest party rock Dj the world has ever seen.
